Package ohos.aafwk.ability

Class Form

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.aafwk.ability.Form
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class Form
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Represents the basic data structure of a form.

    The basic data structure provides details about a form, including the form ID, form name, and the bundle name of the application serving as the form provider. For detailed information about a form, see ProviderFormInfo.

    Since:
    5
